@node sh "What is TestFile"

This stuff is for advanced users only. No value for anybody else.
Test file is an empty executable file.
This file is based on my `Safe` file format.

It is designed to make with it testfiles for AV stuff which contains
only needed stuff (linked or added code etc.)
I decided to share with it because maybe somebody doesn`t want to
make his own test file, but needs it.

The file conatins no any reloc hunks.
The file contains instructions often replaced by hunk increasing viruses.

I hope this will help few people that need to have small database of
linkers, crunchers or even viruses,
in strange combinations to check AV stuff for example...

I`ve prepared few testfiles (of course without virus examples):

FileShield1.2+
PowerPacker4.3
PowerPacker4.3 Library
StoneCracker4.10
StoneCracker4.10 Library
@endnode
